{"tid":1814051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對於捉鬼，我有say，認同幫廣傳","createTime":"2020-01-06T17:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T04:26:17.000Z","uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53dac5b7066b2e578ec02cb085a3d21efac75401","tid":1814051,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:20:35.000Z","msg":"捉鬼捉鬼，其實大家都係想保護手足同將黑狗惡行公諸於世<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但捉到又點?<br />\n信者，你捉唔到都會信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔信的腦殘，你放曬d證據係佢面前，佢都可以睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好亂捉鬼</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由其裝修設計同裝飾的手足<br />\n只要佢攻擊緊對家的商店同人<br />\n就一定唔會係鬼</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">核爆都唔割唔係口號，係態度</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當藍絲為我地所用之際，黑狗為何不可?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢越專業，越大力裝修越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，如果攻擊緊係同路人就要喝止，<br />\n睇下係錯手定有誤會，定真係黑狗所為，<br />\n係電光石火之間，<br />\n不妨試下對佢大叫口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警死全家又好，呀sir開ot都好<br />\n總之越難聽越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係手足一定識答下聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係黑狗就睇下你有無面皮去答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔識答就真係要留意住佢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n黑狗死全家，死完爸爸死媽媽，死完男家死女家"},{"pid":"ebe203ebfcb463c393e58d13c524fa0ddb4fd2f9","tid":1814051,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:24:52.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"5e534e88be10894de1257a9feeaf36e3fa5bb62c","tid":1814051,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:12:23.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"e3f3c2386a766fa34dc702e76e4b5ba2e2bea9c5","tid":1814051,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T18:34:27.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"e09b19e102efbbea2c9a90a019467cf789790b37","tid":1814051,"uid":280899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:26:17.000Z","msg":"推4"}]}